      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Assessment of test sample representativeness is not required at MRL 2. The FDA inter-laboratory dataset used for validation was collected across multiple laboratories with multiple pump specimens, providing inherent sample diversity."
    },
